	module.exports = "<section class=\"intro\" id=\"introduksjon\">\n<h1 class=\"intro\" id=\"introduksjon\">Introduksjon</h1>\n<p>La oss lage et spill: Hangman! Datamaskinen vil velge et ord og du kan\ngjette det bokstav for bokstav. Dersom du gjetter feil for mange\nganger taper du.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"activity\" id=\"steg-1-velg-et-ord\">\n<h1 class=\"activity\" id=\"steg-1-velg-et-ord\">Steg 1: Velg et ord</h1>\n<p>Frst m vi f datamaskinen til  velge et tilfeldig ord, s la oss begynne.</p>\n<section class=\"check\" id=\"sjekkliste\">\n<h2 class=\"check\" id=\"sjekkliste\">Sjekkliste</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>pne IDLE, og pne et nytt vindu</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Skriv inn flgende kode:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> random <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> choice\n\nword = choice([<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"kode\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"kurs\"</span>])\n\nprint(word)\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Lagre programmet ditt og kjr det. Hvilket ord skrives ut?</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Kjr programmet en gang til. Skriver det ut et annet ord?</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Hver gang du kjrer dette programmet vil det velge et tilfeldig ord fra listen <code>[&quot;kode&quot;, &quot;kurs&quot;]</code> ved hjelp av <code>choice</code>-funksjonen.</p>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"activity\" id=\"steg-2-gjett-en-bokstav\">\n<h1 class=\"activity\" id=\"steg-2-gjett-en-bokstav\">Steg 2: Gjett en bokstav</h1>\n<p>N har vi valgt et ord, la oss finne ut hvordan vi gjetter en bokstav.</p>\n<section class=\"check\" id=\"sjekkliste-2\">\n<h2 class=\"check\" id=\"sjekkliste-2\">Sjekkliste</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>I den samme filen, endre koden s den ser ut som flger</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> random <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> choice\n\nword = choice([<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"kode\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"kurs\"</span>])\n\nout = <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> letter <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> word:\n    out = out + <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"_\"</span>\n\nprint(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Gjett en bokstav i ordet:\"</span>, out)\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Lagre og kjr programmet.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<figure>Du burde se <code>Gjett en bokstav i ordet: ____</code>, i output-vinduet (det andre vinduet, ikke vinduet du har skrevet programmet ditt i).</figure>\n<p>Vi bruker en <code>for</code>-lkke for  bygge en tekst hvor hver bokstav i ordet er byttet med en understrek <code>_</code>. Ordet <code>kode</code> vil da for eksempel skrives som <code>____</code> til skjermen.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>La oss gjette p en bokstav! Endre koden s den ser ut som dette</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> random <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> choice\n\nword = choice([<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"kode\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"kurs\"</span>])\n\nout = <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> letter <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> word:\n    out = out + <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"_\"</span>\n\nprint(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Gjett en bokstav i ordet, avslutt med enter:\"</span>, out)\n\nguess = input()\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> guess <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> word:\n    print(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Yay\"</span>)\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span>:\n    print(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Nope\"</span>)\n</code></pre>\n<p>Vi bruker en ny prosedyre <code>input()</code> for  finne ut hvilken bokstav spilleren skriver. Vi bruker <code>if</code> for  sjekke om bokstaven er i ordet.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Da har vi gjort det viktigste, la oss fortsette videre.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"protip\" id=\"python-2-tips\">\n<h2 class=\"protip\" id=\"python-2-tips\">Python 2 tips:</h2>\n<p>Bruk <code>raw_input</code> i stedet for <code>input</code> dersom du bruker en gammel\nversion av python.</p>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"activity\" id=\"steg-3-husk-bokstavene-som-er-gjettet\">\n<h1 class=\"activity\" id=\"steg-3-husk-bokstavene-som-er-gjettet\">Steg 3: Husk bokstavene som er gjettet</h1>\n<figure>N skal vi bruke to nye komponenter i python, lister og <code>while</code>-lkker.</figure>\n<section class=\"check\" id=\"sjekkliste-3\">\n<h2 class=\"check\" id=\"sjekkliste-3\">Sjekkliste</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>I den samme filen, endre koden s den ser slik ut:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> random <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> choice\n\nword = choice([<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"kode\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"kurs\"</span>])\n\nguessed = []\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">while</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">True</span>:\n    out = <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"\"</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> letter <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> word:\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> letter <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> guessed:\n            out = out + letter\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span>:\n            out = out + <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"_\"</span>\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> out == word:\n        print(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Du gjettet\"</span>, word)\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>\n\n\n    print(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Gjett en bokstav i ordet:\"</span>, out)\n    guess = input()\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> guess <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> guessed:\n        print(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Bokstaven er allerede gjettet p:\"</span>, guess)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">elif</span> guess <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> word:\n        print(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Yay\"</span>)\n        guessed.append(guess)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span>:\n        print(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Nope\"</span>)\n\n    print()\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Kjr koden og prv  gjette bokstavene.</p>\n<p>Vi har laget en <code>while True</code>-lkke, tilsvarende <code>for alltid</code> i scratch. Denne vil i utgangspunktet fortsette  sprre spilleren om  gjette bokstaver for alltid. For  komme ut av lkken bruker vi kommandoen <code>break</code> nr ordet har blitt gjettet.</p>\n<figure>Vi bruker ogs en liste, <code>guessed</code>, hvor vi legger til bokstavene som er riktige for  huske dem senere.</figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"activity\" id=\"steg-4-tell-feilene\">\n<h1 class=\"activity\" id=\"steg-4-tell-feilene\">Steg 4: Tell feilene</h1>\n<figure>For at Hangman skal holde oversikt over alle bokstavene som er gjettet\np m vi ogs huske p nr spilleren gjetter feil.</figure>\n<section class=\"check\" id=\"sjekkliste-4\">\n<h2 class=\"check\" id=\"sjekkliste-4\">Sjekkliste</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Endre filen du jobber med slik at den blir seende ut som dette:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> random <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> choice\n\nword = choice([<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"kode\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"kurs\"</span>])\n\nguessed = []\nwrong = []\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">while</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">True</span>:\n    out = <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"\"</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> letter <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> word:\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> letter <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> guessed:\n            out = out + letter\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span>:\n            out = out + <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"_\"</span>\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> out == word:\n        print(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Du gjettet\"</span>, word)\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>\n\n    print(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Gjett en bokstav i ordet:\"</span>, out)\n\n    guess = input()\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> guess <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> guessed <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">or</span> guess <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> wrong:\n        print(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Bokstaven er allerede gjettet p:\"</span>, guess)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">elif</span> guess <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> word:\n        print(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Yay\"</span>)\n        guessed.append(guess)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span>:\n        print(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Nope\"</span>)\n        wrong.append(guess)\n\n    print()\n</code></pre>\n<figure>Vi bruker en ny liste <code>wrong</code> som tar vare p alle bokstavene vi har gjettet som er feil.</figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"activity\" id=\"steg-5-bare-noen-fa-forsok\">\n<h1 class=\"activity\" id=\"steg-5-bare-noen-fa-forsok\">Steg 5: Bare noen f forsk</h1>\n<figure>Bare en ting gjenstr fr spillet er ferdig, vi vil begrense hvor\nmange forsk man har til  gjette.</figure>\n<section class=\"check\" id=\"sjekkliste-5\">\n<h2 class=\"check\" id=\"sjekkliste-5\">Sjekkliste</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<figure>Endre filen for  legge til en ny variabel, <code>tries</code>:</figure>\n<pre><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> random <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> choice\n\nword = choice([<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"kode\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"kurs\"</span>])\n\nguessed = []\nwrong = []\n\ntries = <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">while</span> tries &gt; <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>:\n    out = <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"\"</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> letter <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> word:\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> letter <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> guessed:\n            out = out + letter\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span>:\n            out = out + <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"_\"</span>\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> out == word:\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>\n\n    print(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Gjett en bokstav i ordet:\"</span>, out)\n    print(tries, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"forsk igjen\"</span>)\n\n    guess = input()\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> guess <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> guessed <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">or</span> guess <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> wrong:\n        print(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Bokstaven er allerede gjettet p:\"</span>, guess)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">elif</span> guess <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> word:\n        print(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Yay\"</span>)\n        guessed.append(guess)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span>:\n        print(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Nope\"</span>)\n        tries = tries - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>\n        wrong.append(guess)\n\n    print()\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> tries:\n    print(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Du gjettet\"</span>, word)\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span>:\n    print(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Du klarte ikke  gjette\"</span>, word)\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Kjr programmet, og se hva som skjer nr du gjetter feil bokstaver.</p>\n<p>Legg merke til at vi endret <code>while</code>-lkken ved  legge inn en forutsetning, <code>while tries &gt; 0</code>. Dette betyr at lkken bare kjres s lenge variabelen <code>tries</code> er strre enn 0. Kikker du litt rundt i koden ser du at <code>tries</code> starter med verdien 7, ogs blir den 1 mindre for hver feil bokstav som gjettes. Alts vil spilleren kunne gjette opp til 7 bokstaver feil fr spillet er slutt.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"activity\" id=\"steg-6-legg-til-nye-ord\">\n<h1 class=\"activity\" id=\"steg-6-legg-til-nye-ord\">Steg 6: Legg til nye ord</h1>\n<section class=\"check\" id=\"sjekkliste-6\">\n<h2 class=\"check\" id=\"sjekkliste-6\">Sjekkliste</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Finn linjen i programkoden som sier:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-python\">word = choice([<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"kode\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"kurs\"</span>])\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Vi kan endre denne linjen for  legge til flere ord i spillet. Prv for eksempel</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-python\">word = choice([<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"kode\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"kurs\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"robot\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"klubb\"</span>])\n</code></pre>\n<p>Husk at ordene m st i anfrselstegn og at det m vre komma mellom ordene for  lage en liste. Legg til flere ord som du finner p selv.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</section>\n";

