	module.exports = "<section class=\"intro\" id=\"introduksjon\">\n<h1 class=\"intro\" id=\"introduksjon\">Introduksjon</h1>\n<p>Lr  legge til lyd og video p din nettside!</p>\n<p>Det finnes flere mte  legge til lyd, bilder og video p nettsidene dine. La oss ta en titt p de sammen.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"activity\" id=\"legg-til-video-fra-youtube\">\n<h1 class=\"activity\" id=\"legg-til-video-fra-youtube\">Legg til video fra YouTube</h1>\n<p> legge til enn video fra YouTube er veldig lett.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>G til videoen sin side p YouTube</li>\n<li>Under videospilleren finner du en <code>Del</code>/<code>Share</code> knapp. Trykk p den.</li>\n<li>For  f kode du kan bruke p nettsiden din, trykk <code>Embed</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Koden vil ligne p dette:</p>\n<pre><code>&lt;<span class=\"hljs-tag\">iframe</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"560\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">height</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"315\"</span> src=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"//www.youtube.com/embed/FjgQbPwkljQ\"</span> frameborder=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"0\"</span> allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<p>Denne kodesnutten vil legge til en kodeklubbvideo p siden din. Kopier koden og lim din der du vil at videoen skal vises. Legg merke til <code>width</code>(bredde) og <code>height</code>(hyde) attributtene. De gjr at du kan bestemme hvor stort videoen skal  vises p nettsiden. Forsk gjerne  forandre p de.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"activity\" id=\"legg-til-en-video-fra-vimeo\">\n<h1 class=\"activity\" id=\"legg-til-en-video-fra-vimeo\">Legg til en video fra Vimeo.</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>G p videosiden p Vimeo.</li>\n<li>Klikk p <code>Del</code>/<code>Share</code> knappen i videospilleren.</li>\n<li>Nederst vises det en boks med <em>Embed</em>. Klikk p den og kopiere koden. Koden vil ligne p dette:</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code>&lt;<span class=\"hljs-tag\">iframe</span> src=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"http://player.vimeo.com/video/44738167?title=0&amp;amp;byline=0&amp;amp;portrait=0&amp;amp;badge=0\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"600\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">height</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"338\"</span> frameborder=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"0\"</span> webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>Lim inn koden der du vil at videoen skal vises p siden. Legg merke til <code>width</code>(bredde) og <code>height</code>(hyde) attributtene. De gjr at du kan bestemme hvor stort videoen skal  vises p nettsiden. Forsk gjerne  forandre p de.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"activity\" id=\"legge-til-en-video-fra-datamaskinen-din\">\n<h1 class=\"activity\" id=\"legge-til-en-video-fra-datamaskinen-din\">Legge til en video fra datamaskinen din</h1>\n<p>Hvis du har en video du har laget kan du legge den til p siden din uten  laste den opp p YouTube eller Vimeo.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>For  legge til en video p siden din m du legge til en <code>video</code> tag. Akkurat som <code>img</code> taggen har ogs video en <code>src</code> attributt som peker p filen:</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">video</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip_landing.mp4\"</span>&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-title\">video</span>&gt;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Det som er kjedelig nr man legger til video er at ikke aller nettleserene klarer  spille av alle videoformatene. <code>.mp4</code> og <code>.ogv</code> fungere i de fleste nettleserene, s det kan lnne seg  lagre videoen din i et av de formatene.</p>\n<p>For  la nettleseren vite at vi har flere formater tilgjengelig, kan vi skrive flgende kode:</p>\n<pre><code>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">video</span>&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">source</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip_landing.ogv\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"video/ogg\"</span>&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">source</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip_landing.mp4\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"video/mp4\"</span>&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-title\">video</span>&gt;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>For  legge til et bilde som vises fr videoen spilles av, kan du bruke 'poster' attributtet p videotaggen:</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">video</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">poster</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip_landing.jpg\"</span>&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">source</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip_landing.ogv\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"video/ogg\"</span>&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">source</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip_landing.mp4\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"video/mp4\"</span>&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-title\">video</span>&gt;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>Hvis du vil at videoen automatisk skal start  spilles av kan du legge til <code>autoplay</code> attributtet. Det gjres p denne mten:</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">video</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">poster</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip_landing.jpg\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">autoplay</span>&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">source</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip_landing.ogv\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"video/ogg\"</span>&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">source</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip_landing.mp4\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"video/mp4\"</span>&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-title\">video</span>&gt;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>For  vise knapper til  styre videoen med, snn som spill av, pause, volum og s videre kan du legge til <code>controls</code> attributtet:</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">video</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">poster</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip_landing.jpg\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">controls</span>&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">source</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip_landing.ogv\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"video/ogg\"</span>&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">source</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip_landing.mp4\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"video/mp4\"</span>&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-title\">video</span>&gt;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>Du kan ogs styre strrelsen p videoen med <code>width</code>(bredde) og <code>height</code>(hyde) attributtene p flgende mte:</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">video</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">poster</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip_landing.jpg\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"600\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">height</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"400\"</span>&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">source</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip_landing.ogv\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"video/ogg\"</span>&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">source</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip_landing.mp4\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"video/mp4\"</span>&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-title\">video</span>&gt;</span>\n</code></pre>\n</section>\n<section class=\"activity\" id=\"legg-til-en-lydfil-fra-datamaskinen-din\">\n<h1 class=\"activity\" id=\"legg-til-en-lydfil-fra-datamaskinen-din\">Legg til en lydfil fra datamaskinen din</h1>\n<p>Mten man legger lydfiler til p nettsiden din er ganske lik mten man legger til videoer p.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>For  legge til en lydfil kan du skrive dette:</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">audio</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip.mp3\"</span>&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-title\">audio</span>&gt;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<figure>Legg merke til <code>src</code> attributtet som peker p filen.</figure>\n<p>Akkurat som med video er det ikke alle nettlesere som kan spille alle type lydfiler. For  srge for at flest mulig kan hre p filen br du legge den til i flere formater. <code>.mp3</code> og <code>.oga</code> er formatene som flest nettlesere klarer  spille av.</p>\n<pre><code>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">audio</span>&gt;</span>\n     <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">source</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip.mp3\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">'audio/mp3'</span>&gt;</span>\n     <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">source</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip.ogg\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">'audio/ogg; codecs=vorbis'</span>&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-title\">audio</span>&gt;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>For  legge til knapper for  styre lydavspillingen m du legge til <code>controls</code> attributtet:</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">audio</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">controls</span>&gt;</span>\n     <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">source</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip.mp3\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">'audio/mp3'</span>&gt;</span>\n     <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">source</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip.ogg\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">'audio/ogg; codecs=vorbis'</span>&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-title\">audio</span>&gt;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>Hvis du nsker at lyden skal starte  spilles av med en gang man gr inn p nettsiden kan du legge til <code>autoplay</code> attributten p denn mten:</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code>  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">audio</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">controls</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">autoplay</span>&gt;</span>\n     <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">source</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip.mp3\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">'audio/mp3'</span>&gt;</span>\n     <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title\">source</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">\"romskip.ogg\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-value\">'audio/ogg; codecs=vorbis'</span>&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-title\">audio</span>&gt;</span>\n</code></pre>\n</section>\n";

